column4: NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "3B7C4AB94D95FF21DA7A018304DC9717", "We should hide from them and wait, then come back. It\'s twelve o\'clock.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "388FA31F422B03837B50839F3C3CE124", "Wow, he\'s staring at us! Maybe he\'s suspicious about us.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "90331E564930697F15B00994BF6673CF", "This factory must be draining their waste to sewage. I must find out.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "7611F923404179C60AF6F29E17764C4B", "You can\'t go thru here without a permit issued by the person in charge.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "2F2A7DAB406C90D1B55BFBB1A2F5F985", "OK, if that\'s the way it is.")

column13: ((21, NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "0D4095D3490144FD9B4E3BA56A25D377", "Time for shift change")),(31, NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "2E9320694DA040864A84F880BA82E3B0", "Let me thru or else")),(37, NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "26935E4E49DF26F01C9919B3AFF0925E", "No, nothing")))

column4: NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "3C846AEA471CCCD7EBDCC5B20A5D66DB", "It\'s not the time for the shift change yet.")

column13: ((24, NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "A2CB2C544462ABD84325F4951DC3046B", "That\'s OK, don\'t worry.")),(27, NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "1E2E10254269C0E56C6ABE92D3821410", "When is shift change?")))

column4: NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "048853CF41A980EB8133F8BE9401DBF6", "No, we have to follow the time strictly.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "44C79B9742BA8F9862A377856ED1B31F", "The shift changes are at midnight and noon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "ED7D5CEA4547EA52DF6B6FB0E8688B88", "You can\'t threaten me. You have to get a permit.")

column13: ((34, NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "0BA8077D401B3A1C52459E895515E079", "A permit? I got one.")),(35, NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "F31C2E71445F91715858B8A8A6DD234C", "I\'ll give you permission!")))

column4: NSLOCTEXT("[2DA156F040287BB7CC6A84A2C759A27A]", "776B25794D3A1378B53FB291D1EF4831", "We can\'t give you a permit. You have to go thru proper channels.")
